==English==

===Etymology===
From {{der|en|ang|þanon}} + adverbial genitive ending {{m|ang|-es}}, the former from a {{der|en|gem-pro|-}} root ''*þan-''. Cognate with [[w|Westphalian]] Low German {{l|nds|diëne}}.

